<p>Ok, SLAM is a skill that takes a sheild to use. The char taked the sheild and hits the mob up side the head stunning him, so to speak. The only race to not need a sheild is the Ogar because of their FAT body. They were given the skill to &quot;sit on the mob&quot;, err, SLAM with thier body and no sheild was required. Yes other race/classes can get it with AAs. As a Bez you are not ment to have the SLAM skill. You probably had it at lower level if they over looked it. But if your looking for a stun hit use your Head Shot skill. <br /></p>
